				<h1 class="page_header">Why Study Philosophy?</h1>
				<div class="html_container intro">
			<p>To <a target="_blank" href="http://undergrad.usc.edu/programs/major/declaring.html">declare a major</a>
 or minor in philosophy, or to add philosophy as a second major/minor, 
visit the Advisement Office at CAS 120 or call them at 213-740-2534.</p>
<h2>Philosophy Pays</h2>
<p>Philosophy prepares you for the kind of rigorous thinking and 
critical analysis used in a wide variety of fields. You might be 
surprised at how well the average mid-career salaries of philosophy 
majors compare to those of other popular majors.</p>
